#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn6.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The Appeal "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Katamodakatissasutta → katamorakatissasuttaṃ (bj) | tissakasuttaṃ (s1-3) | tissako (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Katamodakatissasutta "
msgstr "8. About Katamorakatissaka "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn6.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.8:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā divāvihāragato hoti paṭisallīno. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha had gone into retreat for the day’s meditation. "

msgctxt "sn6.8:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho subrahmā ca paccekabrahmā suddhāvāso ca paccekabrahmā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā paccekaṃ dvārabāhaṃ nissāya aṭṭhaṃsu. "
msgstr "Then the independent brahmās Subrahmā and Suddhāvāsa went to the Buddha and stationed themselves one by each door-post. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: katamodakatissakaṃ → katamorakatissaṃ (bj) | katamorakatissakaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn6.8:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho suddhāvāso paccekabrahmā katamodakatissakaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Suddhāvāsa recited this verse about the mendicant Katamorakatissaka in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.149, sc2
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.1"
msgid "“Appameyyaṃ paminanto, "
msgstr "“What wise person here would judge "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.2"
msgid "Kodha vidvā vikappaye; "
msgstr "the immeasurable by measuring them? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.3"
msgid "Appameyyaṃ pamāyinaṃ, "
msgstr "I think anyone who’d do such a thing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.4"
msgid "Nivutaṃ taṃ maññe akissavan”ti. "
msgstr "must be a fool, wrapped in darkness.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
